{"tid":1052552,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解啲人當年咁憎KD?","createTime":"2019-03-08T11:11:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T14:06:53.000Z","uid":200389,"like":5,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ed891017bf3a9070bb1c8cee2c4a8778ff15b4f6","tid":1052552,"uid":200389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:11:14.000Z","msg":"佢本來就唔係celtics球迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁多年嚟爲celtics都獻出所有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算之後佢同奧尼爾不和都只不過係傳聞姐<br />\nKD本人都證實咗同奧尼爾冇野<br />\n根本佢就冇對唔住celtics<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔明點解返到celtics主場嗰陣啲球迷要boo佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年轉會都係為咗生涯可以更上一層樓姐<br />\n講真同咁多一線球星同場個個都想啦 抱咩大腿姐<br />\n事實證明佢真係攞到佢掂都未掂過嘅冠軍喎<br />\n佢當年離隊嘅選擇根本冇做錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82bce87981243d2799f1581523ecd57fd4eda87e","tid":1052552,"uid":26445,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"樓主打錯?KG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b54c1ea811b3d61c0882b4ccdf974a777bc26d8","tid":1052552,"uid":207050,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:12:31.000Z","msg":"KG啊 傻閪"},{"pid":"1f991a2ab2146e6e390dd030a1687278ce3e6578","tid":1052552,"uid":92278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"請問永遠點解"},{"pid":"83def74557ef132213174ef35b47e2b50162a976","tid":1052552,"uid":30773,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:13:01.000Z","msg":"咩撚野kd celtics呀大哥"},{"pid":"0c75b7b057070bc43c32f718d3c66621b05f1cb2","tid":1052552,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:13:30.000Z","msg":"Kg定kd阿"},{"pid":"badafa85f2ec681ae302ad154694afd439df50c